{"tid":1147895,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★返工=?? 技工修冷氣墮斃　童軍總會被票控判罰款2萬","createTime":"2019-05-10T06:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T17:19:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"719e7a3a569a06a2350a6dd121e0561d7216aca2","tid":1147895,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:14:35.000Z","msg":"一名技工去年8月26日在香港童軍總會洞梓童軍中心，爬上一條梯維修冷氣時，失足從1.5米高處墮地受傷，送院後最終不治。香港童軍總會事後被票控沒有確保僱員的安全及健康罪，今(10日)在沙田法院認罪，罰款2萬港元。<br />\n<br />\n辯方求情時形容該案是不幸事件，會方有百多年歷史，未曾干犯同類情況。會方本有兩名維修工人，其中一人放假，因而留下事主獨自工作。總會對失去工人感到悔咎，向家屬致以慰問，並成立小組檢討事件並提高工程安全意識。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190510/bkn-20190510132712959-0510_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190510%2Fbkn-20190510132712959-0510_00822_001.html&d=7bK604G145JEtCxDEZ4NGlwLDRbgpiba54y0vEBNjMo%3D&h=b62a4b1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190510/bkn-20190510132712959-0510_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"85a7480dbc304099b2afb9da3f7f02157a0968a0","tid":1147895,"uid":19454,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:15:06.000Z","msg":"$20,000=返工Life"},{"pid":"bd06524e2dc7e7ec9a5f40a90434221bccbeeb53","tid":1147895,"uid":220701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:18:03.000Z","msg":"一條人命=$20000"},{"pid":"d8a93499ed3f484f4bfb5ca991e036a28ac7884f","tid":1147895,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:18:44.000Z","msg":"技工2萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2829cc4f79e6b7796a18941f895b12679a15c0e","tid":1147895,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:24:10.000Z","msg":"不如改做定額罰款啦"},{"pid":"f3b6f490ff6f8a60bc95c1d78c7fc3087ffebc58","tid":1147895,"uid":166792,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T06:25:15.000Z","msg":"罰技工一個月人工 完"},{"pid"